commitResults.messageTitle: Level-0: Renamed chatbot, changed greeting and exit message
Level-1: 1. Consolidated standard Greeting and Bye message into separate Messages class
commitResults.messageBody:
2. Introduced "echo" feature: Malenia will echo back whatever the user types

3. Introduced "bye" feature: The user will can exit the chatbot by typing "bye"

commitResults.messageTitle: Level-2: 1. Added ability to add to a list: Any entry from the user will be added to a list
commitResults.messageBody: 2. Added ability to display the list: Typing "list" will display all contents of the list

commitResults.messageTitle: Level-3: 1. Added ability to mark and unmark tasks
commitResults.messageBody: 2. The list display of the tasks now show the marked status of each task

commitResults.messageTitle: Level-4: Added categiries to tasks (Todo, Deadline, Event)
Added custom Exceptions class for Malenia
Incorporated custom Exception errors to the main code
Put all classes into packages and added "task" package
